    FM->>UI: Vehicle status update<br/>{status: OUT_OF_SERVICE, reason: FALLBACK}
    UI->>SO: **NOTIFICATION**<br/>Vehicle AV-001 in MRC<br/>Inspection required

    %% AUDIT & COMPLIANCE
    Note over AUTO,SO: AUDIT & COMPLIANCE
